                "image": {
                    "type": "image",
                    "name": "Additional Lore",
                    "image": "Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png"
                },
                "html": "Nuckelavees are equally delighted to murder and feed upon both hapless peasants and altruistic naturalists engaged in the process of cleaning up pollution. Indeed, those who would seek to purify such sites are often regarded as the greater threat by a nuckelavee, as without a befouled land to dwell in, the foul fey would wither away."
            }
